### Health check
GET http://localhost:8003/test

### Listar todas las reservas
GET http://localhost:8003/reservas

### Obtener reserva por ID
GET http://localhost:8003/reservas/1

### Reservas de un cliente
GET http://localhost:8003/reservas/cliente/1

### Crear reserva
POST http://localhost:8003/reservas
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "cliente_id": 1,
    "vehiculo_id": 1,
    "fecha_inicio": "2025-06-01",
    "fecha_fin": "2025-06-07"
}

### Completar reserva
PATCH http://localhost:8003/reservas/1/estado
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "estado": "completada"
}

### Cancelar reserva
PATCH http://localhost:8003/reservas/1/estado
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "estado": "cancelada"
}

### Eliminar reserva
DELETE http://localhost:8003/reservas/1
